                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 152.) I was on duty, and heard a cry of "Stop thief"—I ran after the prisoner, and overtook him—I searched, but found nothing on him—a baker picked up a pair of boots about two yards from the prisoner, and about a quarter of a mile from the shop—I had run five or six hundred yardshe was taken by another man.</p>
